    <stitle>FRONT STEER AXLE: EATON EFA-12 - REMOVE/DISASSEMBLE</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcsubsec>
        <title>REMOVE/DISASSEMBLE</title>
        <svcproc svcproctype="remove" graphiccount="0">
            <title>OVERHAUL PRELIMINARY STEPS</title>
            <para>Prior to performing overhaul procedures, the following preliminary steps should be accomplished.
            </para>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Set parking brake and block drive wheels to prevent vehicle movement.</para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Jack vehicle until steering axle wheels are raised from the ground. Support raised
                    vehicle with safety stands.
                </para>
                <specpara>
                    <warning>
                        <para>Never work under a vehicle supported only by a jack.</para>
                    </warning>
                </specpara>
            </step1>
        </svcproc>
    </svcsubsec>
